what dS in this case is.

00:03:02.180 --> 00:03:04.850
And it's just a d theta dz.

00:03:04.850 --> 00:03:07.100
So let me write
down what I'm going

00:03:07.100 --> 00:03:09.970
to need to completely determine
the rest of number one

00:03:09.970 --> 00:03:13.460
