00:05:13.758 --> 00:05:15.030
but I'll give you the answer.

00:05:15.030 --> 00:05:17.770
So let me write down the answer.

00:05:17.770 --> 00:05:26.230
You get a h squared over
2, plus a squared h over 2.

00:05:26.230 --> 00:05:28.500
So that's the solution
you actually get.

00:05:28.500 --> 00:05:31.524
So again, I mean, you have to
