00:07:48.030 --> 00:07:50.920
So a squared times z
divided by a is a times z.

00:07:50.920 --> 00:07:53.880
And now, if I want to use
the right coordinates,

00:07:53.880 --> 00:07:55.510
think about theta and phi.

00:07:55.510 --> 00:07:58.280
z is a cosine phi.

00:07:58.280 --> 00:08:00.440
So F dot n in the
coordinates I'm interested in

00:08:00.440 --> 00:08:02.990
